{"tid":796374,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人明點解我女朋友咁鍾意去人地到訓","createTime":"2018-08-27T17:59:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T18:56:10.000Z","uid":74823,"like":3,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9207d2320ddc0fa376bcfbcf974017cd84c26858","tid":796374,"uid":74823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T17:59:11.000Z","msg":"以下提及既所有人都係女仔 包括樓豬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/28/015534_3ae13317ca0fee97da78845830b199e2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F28%2F015534_3ae13317ca0fee97da78845830b199e2.png&h=29fd55c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我女朋友間唔時就會去人地屋企過夜 佢話覺得人地屋企舒服 <br />\n<br />\n有時有埋佢朋友屋企人係間屋 有時無 有時佢單獨去有時一班人<br />\n<br />\n雖然話大家都係女仔 我都100%相信我條女同佢啲朋友係無野既 我都識佢啲女仔朋友 <br />\n<br />\n但問心我都幾介意佢去人地到訓 第一我最怕佢同人地訓埋同人張床 因為我唔鍾意佢同其他女仔有身體接觸<br />\n<br />\n第二 我擔心我咁信任佢 遲早有日咁樣會帶帽<br />\n<br />\n其實係我太小心眼 定佢唔識避忌呢？<br />\n<br />\n因為我唔會阻止佢地出去玩出去食飯 純粹唔鍾意佢地一齊過夜<br />\n<br />\n利申埋 我唔係tb 唔想係呢到討論tb/基佬死全家既觀念"},{"pid":"9327c07bb0141e78bff95f5782bc825f998ce972","tid":796374,"uid":19126,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:01:11.000Z","msg":"我前度都成日周圍訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n放心，冇事，拍哂心口保證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afa678fef29073c89a736c07df2cc39ee7927680","tid":796374,"uid":184233,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:01:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">帽事嘅</span>"},{"pid":"8762f2cf9d8388fdf235990d20946e7bf78a215f","tid":796374,"uid":74823,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9327c07bb0141e78bff95f5782bc825f998ce972","tid":796374,"uid":19126,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:01:11.000Z","msg":"我前度都成日周圍訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n放心，冇事，拍哂心口保證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:01:34.000Z","msg":"你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要變埋前度"},{"pid":"8c8e0cafe6e6fb1cd98b08ca0f7c57ce78b0f252","tid":796374,"uid":74823,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"afa678fef29073c89a736c07df2cc39ee7927680","tid":796374,"uid":184233,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:01:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">帽事嘅</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:02:01.000Z","msg":"我覺得現階段又唔會 遲啲我都唔敢保證"},{"pid":"8cecd6c66fa680b43207e39e9568102c19c680d8","tid":796374,"uid":74823,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:09:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"07798bf8b14cf450e5f82a2d07c8cba682b4741f","tid":796374,"uid":182195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:15:09.000Z","msg":"咁都忍到，比著我會擔心自己帽咗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a286a124a16ef7509a216fd55f1ce29f3565b0","tid":796374,"uid":74823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07798bf8b14cf450e5f82a2d07c8cba682b4741f","tid":796374,"uid":182195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:15:09.000Z","msg":"咁都忍到，比著我會擔心自己帽咗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T18:21:51.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得唔會帽 真係純粹朋友個種<br />\n<br />\n係心難受"},{"pid":"33d4058f3648e242c8923ff4d5d29852edf0136d","tid":796374,"uid":182195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3a286a124a16ef7509a216fd55f1ce29f3565b0","tid":796374,"uid":74823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07798bf8b14cf450e5f82a2d07c8cba682b4741f","tid":796374,"uid":182195